					"type": 23,
					"value": "This is dialogue played by the ward device placed on the wall in Devil's Fee.\r\nIt resembles the head of the imp or the devil.\r\nWhen the player resolves the puzzle by combining this head device with any liquid bottle ward disables the trap and throws this AD. It will repeat it when clicked."
